 holes spins rapidly, spin-alignment during binary mergers\n(rather than prolonged accretion) could be responsible for spin-ups.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 31 Jan 2008 22:34:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 27 May 2008 19:50:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-11-11"}
