y, as is verified by numerical time-dependent Schr\\\"{o}dinger equation\nsimulation of a Xe atom shined by a combination of IR and XUV field.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 Feb 2008 15:32:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-02-04"}
